text: Emily Bonser (born 27 October 1995) is a retired Australian rules footballer who played for West Coast in the AFL Women's (AFLW). ==AFLW career== Bonser joined West Coast for their inaugural season. At the end of the season, Bonser retired from football for personal reasons. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:West Coast Eagles (AFLW) players Category:Australian rules footballers from Western Australia Category:Sportswomen from Western Australia
